      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ZIPPING PERCAT (8) held a forward position from the pinch but began to paddle on the bend and drifted out of the finish when 8th at Wentworth Park in Maiden company. Safe beginner but wide box to overcome and will need some luck. Worth another chance. ZIPPING LOWENS (7) has missed the placings at his last couple but was in the money three back when second (30.46) at Wentworth Park in a Maiden. Expected to bounce back to best. MINDARIBBA (1) is overdue for a maiden success having placed at three of 11 starts, the latest missing the frame when sixth at Taree Super Track. Good beginner assisted by the inside draw. Can measure up this time. KUNG FU ETHICS (5) was in the money last start and poses a threat again.",
